```py
SELECT fullname,
       managerID,
       joining_date,
       city,
       COUNT(*)
FROM employee_details
GROUP BY fullname,
         managerID,
         joining_date,
         city
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
```

```py
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM (
SELECT user_id,
       COUNT(event_date_time) AS image_per_user
FROM event_log
GROUP BY user_id AS image_per_user
WHERE image_per_user < 2000
  AND image_per_user > 1000;
```
